00:06:14.940 --> 00:06:18.191
We'd meet, we'd exchange cards, and then actually
a little bit later in the conference, they'd

00:06:18.191 --> 00:06:19.740
come up to me and say, "Wow!

00:06:19.740 --> 00:06:21.040
I just checked out your website.

00:06:21.040 --> 00:06:22.570
I saw what you're doing.

00:06:22.570 --> 00:06:23.570
That's amazing!

00:06:23.570 --> 00:06:24.600
How did you do it?"

00:06:24.600 --> 00:06:29.340
I'm just kind of laughing because that's a
whole lot of work.

00:06:29.340 --> 00:06:31.370
A lot of people think that it happens overnight.

00:06:31.370 --> 00:06:34.259
Now, people are looking for that quick fix;
it's not.

00:06:34.259 --> 00:06:39.759
You've got to be able to take action and know
that you're going to run into failure, and

00:06:39.759 --> 00:06:42.310
be steady, consistent.

00:06:42.310 --> 00:06:46.560
We do this in college and we need to be continue
doing this throughout life, gentlemen.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:51.220
We do this up through school and it's something
that I think a lot of us lose whenever we

00:06:51.220 --> 00:06:54.620
get out because we're putting this unstructured
environment.

00:06:54.620 --> 00:06:55.660
Create structure for yourself.

00:06:55.660 --> 00:07:01.110
One of the things I did is hire a business
coach and she makes sure that I do stay on

00:07:01.110 --> 00:07:06.490
path to the path where I'm headed, but once
you do it, gentlemen, amazing things happen.

